Lot No. 1818, Pls-93

A PARCEL OF LAND (Lot No. 1818, Pls-93), situated in Poblacion, Municipality of Tabuk, Province of Kalinga-Apayao, Island of Luzon. Bounded on the South along line 1-2 by Road; on the West along lines 2-3-4-5-6-7-8 by 3.00 m. wide legal easement and by Lays Creek; on the North along line 8-9 by Road 15.00 m. wide; and on the East along line 9-1 by Road 10.00 m. wide. Beginning at a point marked “1” of Lot No. 1818, Pls-93, being N. 12 deg. 17′ W., 449.25 m. from BLLM #20, Pls-93.

