point of beginning, containing an area of FIVE THOUSAND SEVEN HUNDRED AND EIGHTY ONE (5,781) SQUARE METERS. All points are marked on the ground as follows: points 1, 2, 8 and 9 by BL Cyl. Conc. Mons. and the rest by Stakes. Bearings true. These lots were surveyed in accordance with law and existing regulations promulgated thereunder by S.G. Peres, Geodetic Engineer, on August 30, 1946.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF, I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

Done in the City of Manila, this 27th day of June in the year of Our Lord, nineteen hundred and eighty-eight.

(Sgd.) CORAZON C. AQUINO

By the President: (Sgd.) CATALINO MACARAIG, JR. Executive Secretary

